'''"The Uprisings"''' referred to a series of sporadic guerrilla campaigns that took place on the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Ord Cestus/Legends|Ord Cestus]]. Carried out by the [[Desert Wind]] terrorist group against the [[Cestus Cybernetics]] corporation, they began around [[121 BBY]] with a plague that decimated the [[X'Ting]] population. In [[26 BBY/Legends|26 BBY]] they included a [[Mining/Legends|mining]] union strike that Cestus Cybernetics ended using killer [[Droid/Legends|droids]]. They were finally suppressed in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]] however, the next year Desert Wind was remade with help from the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi Order]] and the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]].

